{
  "texts": [
    "\"'In summary, DRaFT-Q presents a simple yet powerful framework that intelligently adapts both model structure and optimization focus during fine-tuning.",
    "It is memory-efficient, scalable, and compatible with quantized training workflows.",
    "As LLMs continue to scale and become more ubiquitous, adaptive PEFT techniques like DRaFT-Q will be critical for enabling broad deployment, personalization, and sustainable AI development.",
    "Example (GSM8K):Question: John has 4 apples, buys 5 more, and gives away 3.",
    "How many does he have?"
  ]
}